  <td width="580" colspan="2" valign="top">
  <!-- Start Update Input -->
  <p>We want it pretty fucking bad. We waxed High Priest early tonite to 
warm up for our insane Emperor kill. What an intense fight. We went up 
there tonite with 60 people, hoping to score a sweet kill and finish off 
the last of our VT keys. Something was to be learned about fighting 
Emperor with 46 people (14 people on CC, and for lack of a better 
term, 'Mad Props' to the CC groups who kept our asses unmolested all 
night), the killing doesnt go fast. In fact, it barely goes at all. The 
fight lasted just over 58 minutes, wow we suck huh? No, actually. It 
seems 
like everything that could go wrong, did go wrong. Loose snakes, dead 
tanks, rampaged clerics, TERRIBLE DPS, all the makings of a horrible 
wipe. 
I dont have a damn clue how we pulled it off, I guess we just wanted it 
that bad.</p>

<p>How close was it? Oh it was close, real close, too close...</p>
<p><img src=http://www.furys-edge.com/news/june22/buhbuh.gif></p>

<p><img src=http://www.furys-edge.com/news/june22/close.gif></p>

<p>It was real messy, but hey, he died and we're all going to 
Disneyla...Vex Thal. Nice job everyone, a truely beautiful recovery.</p>
<p align=center>
<img src=http://www.furys-edge.com/news/june22/emperor1.jpg>
